sourcesContent: import React from 'react' import { Card, Grid, Typography, Button } from '@material-ui/core' import style from './style' const MovieResult = ({ Title, Year, Type, imdbID, Poster, history }) => { const classes = style() const handleSeeMovieDetailClick = event => { history.push(`/movie/${imdbID}`) } return ( {Title} {Year} {Type} ) } export default MovieResult
